00:12:59,923 --> 00:13:01,603
Why don't you protect yourself?

291
00:13:04,244 --> 00:13:05,083
Did you forget?

292
00:13:06,203 --> 00:13:08,004
You promised me before.

293
00:13:10,683 --> 00:13:11,404
You promised...

294
00:13:12,524 --> 00:13:14,164
You promised that you wouldn't
make me worry.

295
00:13:16,284 --> 00:13:18,004
Look at you now.

296
00:13:24,884 --> 00:13:26,284
Honestly, I have something to tell you.

297
00:13:30,843 --> 00:13:32,323
I made up my mind before coming here.

298
00:13:36,884 --> 00:13:37,723
From now onwards,

299
00:13:38,644 --> 00:13:39,923
I won't push you away anymore.

300
00:13:45,960 --> 00:13:52,180
(Earthquake Relief.
Our Nation Stands With Us.)

301
00:14:07,364 --> 00:14:08,484
(It was just a dream.)

302
00:14:11,560 --> 00:14:14,760
♪Look up into the sky and see the light♪

303
00:14:15,200 --> 00:14:17,560
♪It lights up the dark night♪

304
00:14:18,004 --> 00:14:18,683
(No, it's not a dream.)

305
00:14:19,524 --> 00:14:20,284
(It was her.)

306
00:14:25,480 --> 00:14:28,860
♪Leaning on a shoulder♪

307
00:14:28,860 --> 00:14:32,060
♪Burns bright♪

308
00:14:33,923 --> 00:14:34,484
Dr. Zang.

309
00:14:35,484 --> 00:14:36,484
Why are you here in Huining?

310
00:14:36,843 --> 00:14:37,524
When did you arrive?

311
00:14:38,683 --> 00:14:39,404
There's a shortage of workforce
on the frontline.

312
00:14:39,764 --> 00:14:40,803
As a doctor,

313
00:14:41,004 --> 00:14:42,323
it's my duty to help
in the disaster area.

314
00:14:43,004 --> 00:14:43,323
Well.

315
00:14:44,083 --> 00:14:44,764
Besides this reason,

316
00:14:44,803 --> 00:14:45,524
is there another reason?

317
00:14:45,603 --> 00:14:46,644
Is it because of me?

318
00:14:48,364 --> 00:14:49,484
It has nothing to do with you.

319
00:14:50,004 --> 00:14:50,723
If you don't care for me,

320
00:14:50,884 --> 00:14:52,203
why did you come to see me last night?

321
00:14:53,563 --> 00:14:53,884
I...

322
00:14:54,083 --> 00:14:54,843
Says who.

323
00:14:55,124 --> 00:14:55,764
I didn't.

324
00:14:56,364 --> 00:14:57,244
I have the proof.

325
00:14:59,603 --> 00:15:00,083
Give it back to me.

326
00:15:00,364 --> 00:15:00,963
Give it back to me.

327
00:15:01,404 --> 00:15:01,963
Give it back to me.

328
00:15:05,244 --> 00:15:05,963
So, you've admitted this.

329
00:15:09,764 --> 00:15:10,683
I don't care.

330
00:15:11,244 --> 00:15:12,044
I remember

331
00:15:12,044 --> 00:15:12,644
what you said last night.

332
00:15:13,644 --> 00:15:14,164
You said you would never

333
00:15:14,164 --> 00:15:14,764
push me away.

334
00:15:16,244 --> 00:15:16,923
Don't renege

335
00:15:17,443 --> 00:15:18,323
on your word.

336
00:15:20,963 --> 00:15:22,443
Anyway, from today on,

337
00:15:25,083 --> 00:15:26,364
you belong to me.

338
00:15:27,443 --> 00:15:28,004
I'll take good care

339
00:15:28,083 --> 00:15:28,803
of myself

340
00:15:29,284 --> 00:15:29,764
and won't leave you alone

341
00:15:29,963 --> 00:15:30,683
worrying about me.

342
00:15:31,764 --> 00:15:32,404
Please trust me.

343
00:15:34,083 --> 00:15:34,923
I trust you.

344
00:15:39,404 --> 00:15:40,723
Lu Fangqi, I've been looking for you.

345
00:15:40,963 --> 00:15:41,563
We should go now.

346
00:15:42,884 --> 00:15:43,603
I'll be right there.

347
00:15:46,244 --> 00:15:47,323
You must take care of yourself.

348
00:15:47,563 --> 00:15:48,524
I'll come to see you
when I have time.

349
00:15:49,083 --> 00:15:49,683
I'll get going.

350
00:15:50,083 --> 00:15:51,004
Don't come to see me.

351
00:15:51,044 --> 00:15:52,164
I don't want to see you at the hospital.

352
00:15:52,963 --> 00:15:53,524
No, I'll come.

353
00:15:53,843 --> 00:15:54,364
Wait for me.

354
00:15:55,083 --> 00:15:56,284
Take care.

355
00:15:57,884 --> 00:15:58,603
I'll wait for you.

356
00:16:03,920 --> 00:16:09,480
(Earthquake Relief is Our Duty,
Let's Overcome Hardships Together)

357
00:16:12,603 --> 00:16:13,124
Lu Fangqi.

358
00:16:13,404 --> 00:16:14,004
What's wrong with you?

359
00:16:14,923 --> 00:16:15,484
I heard

360
00:16:15,484 --> 00:16:16,284
that your head got hit
a few days ago.

361
00:16:16,803 --> 00:16:17,723
I'm good.

362
00:16:21,364 --> 00:16:22,004
People at the first-aid kiosk

363
00:16:22,164 --> 00:16:23,124
all look worried,

364
00:16:23,364 --> 00:16:24,884
but you look so cheerful.

365
00:16:25,203 --> 00:16:26,323
You grin like a Cheshire cat.

366
00:16:27,484 --> 00:16:28,124
You know nothing.

367
00:16:28,443 --> 00:16:29,764
There's a treasure
in the first-aid kiosk.

368
00:16:30,443 --> 00:16:31,083
What treasure is it?

369
00:16:31,524 --> 00:16:33,124
You've lost your head in the pain.

370
00:16:33,244 --> 00:16:33,923
Treasure, geez.

371
00:16:37,480 --> 00:16:44,580
♪I still vow to protect you♪

372
00:16:44,980 --> 00:16:48,280
♪Right where my heart is♪

373
00:16:48,280 --> 00:16:54,280
♪The warmth of your tenderness resides♪

374
00:17:29,004 --> 00:17:29,603
Let me help you.

375
00:18:02,622 --> 00:18:03,363
Are you going to cry?

376
00:18:03,724 --> 00:18:04,204
No.

377
00:18:04,524 --> 00:18:05,284
You are.

378
00:18:05,284 --> 00:18:05,843
No.

379
00:18:06,444 --> 00:18:07,123
You care for me.

380
00:18:07,123 --> 00:18:07,843
Not at all.

381
00:18:08,363 --> 00:18:08,964
No?

382
00:18:09,044 --> 00:18:09,484
No.

383
00:18:10,363 --> 00:18:11,083
Just minor injuries.

384
00:18:11,484 --> 00:18:12,204
I'm fine.

385
00:18:19,843 --> 00:18:20,563
Fireflies.

386
00:19:32,680 --> 00:19:42,580
(Disaster Relief Supplies)

387
00:19:45,244 --> 00:19:45,684
Sir.

388
00:19:46,643 --> 00:19:47,803
What's the holdup there?

389
00:19:48,403 --> 00:19:49,484
It looks like the road is blocked.

390
00:19:49,684 --> 00:19:50,284
I'll check it out.

391
00:20:11,244 --> 00:20:11,764
Sir.

392
00:20:12,724 --> 00:20:13,563
What's happening up ahead?

393
00:20:13,843 --> 00:20:14,643
The road is blocked.

394
00:20:14,843 --> 00:20:15,883
I can only take you this far.

395
00:20:22,123 --> 00:20:23,524
Thank you.

396
00:20:23,924 --> 00:20:24,403
You're welcome.

397
00:20:39,004 --> 00:20:40,083
(Yu Shishi?)

398
00:20:41,363 --> 00:20:42,044
(It's impossible.)

399
00:20:42,964 --> 00:20:43,964
(Why is she here?)

400
00:20:53,204 --> 00:20:53,964
Why are you here?

401
00:20:54,204 --> 00:20:55,044
I came to find you.

402
00:20:58,764 --> 00:20:59,924
I'm kidding.

403
00:21:02,603 --> 00:21:03,843
I don't have time to talk to you.

404
00:21:04,083 --> 00:21:05,004
Give me a hand.

405
00:21:20,363 --> 00:21:20,764
Here.

406
00:21:20,843 --> 00:21:21,244
Thank you.

407
00:21:21,244 --> 00:21:21,724
Have some water.

408
00:21:41,563 --> 00:21:42,284
Your hand...

409
00:21:44,843 --> 00:21:45,764
They seem rough,

410
00:21:45,964 --> 00:21:47,323
unlike the hands of an actress.

411
00:21:49,403 --> 00:21:50,883
You're not the same one I remember.

412
00:21:51,883 --> 00:21:52,764
I thought...

413
00:21:54,403 --> 00:21:55,843
You thought I couldn't endure hardships

414
00:21:56,724 --> 00:21:57,924
and I was a preppy

415
00:21:58,123 --> 00:21:59,444
and pampered woman.

416
00:22:01,123 --> 00:22:02,603
I did all the action scenes myself,

417
00:22:02,843 --> 00:22:04,484
like fighting, being in the water,

418
00:22:04,643 --> 00:22:05,244
and jumping off buildings

419
00:22:05,284 --> 00:22:06,764
during the filming.

420
00:22:07,484 --> 00:22:08,123
Those scenes

421
00:22:08,123 --> 00:22:09,444
of few seconds you've seen

422
00:22:10,204 --> 00:22:11,163
took me the whole day

423
00:22:11,244 --> 00:22:12,163
and dozens of retakes

424
00:22:12,163 --> 00:22:13,563
to achieve the desired effect.

425
00:22:14,684 --> 00:22:15,764
Do you really think I'm a wallflower?

426
00:22:19,044 --> 00:22:19,964
I just realized

427
00:22:20,803 --> 00:22:21,803
that I didn't really

428
00:22:22,684 --> 00:22:24,123
know you.

429
00:22:38,363 --> 00:22:38,803
You've never

430
00:22:38,964 --> 00:22:40,163
taken a good look at me.

431
00:22:42,204 --> 00:22:43,163
All you can see is...

432
00:22:43,524 --> 00:22:43,964
I have something to attend to.

433
00:22:44,244 --> 00:22:44,764
Got to go now.

434
00:22:45,163 --> 00:22:46,524
Are you going to find Xu Lai?

435
00:22:48,363 --> 00:22:49,083
Don't go.

436
00:22:49,764 --> 00:22:50,524
That's the epicenter.

437
00:22:50,724 --> 00:22:52,323
The roads are collapsed. It's dangerous.

438
00:22:53,004 --> 00:22:54,083
This is my own business.

439
00:22:54,244 --> 00:22:54,803
Don't meddle.

440
00:22:55,204 --> 00:22:56,603
Huo Yanzong. I've told you.

441
00:22:56,684 --> 00:22:58,563
I'm taking care of your matters.

442
00:22:59,563 --> 00:23:01,323
I couldn't reach you.

443
00:23:01,524 --> 00:23:02,803
So, I had to follow the volunteer team

444
00:23:03,004 --> 00:23:04,684
and search for you along the way.

445
00:23:05,163 --> 00:23:06,603
I've been through a lot

446
00:23:07,244 --> 00:23:08,484
in order to find you

447
00:23:08,524 --> 00:23:09,643
and I got bruised all over.

448
00:23:10,163 --> 00:23:10,924
Every time I saw a victim,

449
00:23:11,083 --> 00:23:12,044
I worried

450
00:23:12,204 --> 00:23:13,883
that it might be you.

451
00:23:15,524 --> 00:23:17,524
Now I've found you

452
00:23:17,724 --> 00:23:19,044
and you're leaving.

453
00:23:20,363 --> 00:23:22,204
Even if you meet Xu Lai,

454
00:23:22,563 --> 00:23:23,323
are you sure

455
00:23:23,484 --> 00:23:24,643
she'll go back with you?

456
00:23:28,603 --> 00:23:29,244
Shishi.

457
00:23:30,883 --> 00:23:31,684
Whether or not she goes back

458
00:23:31,843 --> 00:23:32,524
with me,

459
00:23:33,524 --> 00:23:34,403
I must take her back

460
00:23:35,004 --> 00:23:36,123
for her safety.

461
00:23:36,764 --> 00:23:38,484
You're truly hopeless.

462
00:23:39,603 --> 00:23:39,883
Yes.

463
00:23:40,044 --> 00:23:41,004
I'm hopeless.

464
00:23:42,964 --> 00:23:44,244
There is something I must do.

465
00:23:46,484 --> 00:23:46,924
There is someone

466
00:23:47,044 --> 00:23:47,964
I want to protect.

467
00:23:51,244 --> 00:23:52,163
You should go back.

468
00:24:00,724 --> 00:24:02,603
There is someone I want to protect too.

469
00:24:03,044 --> 00:24:03,964
I've made up my mind.

470
00:24:04,484 --> 00:24:05,563
If you insist

471
00:24:05,724 --> 00:24:06,563
on continuing such silly things,

472
00:24:06,764 --> 00:24:07,484
I'll accompany you

473
00:24:07,563 --> 00:24:08,883
and do them with you.

474
00:24:09,163 --> 00:24:10,244
At least you have a partner.

475
00:24:10,603 --> 00:24:11,284
I can take care of you

476
00:24:11,284 --> 00:24:12,323
if anything happens.

477
00:24:12,643 --> 00:24:14,044
As long as you can be safe
while looking for her.

478
00:24:57,643 --> 00:24:58,204
Watch out.

479
00:25:18,444 --> 00:25:19,004
Are you all right?

480
00:26:05,403 --> 00:26:05,964
Shishi.

481
00:26:06,764 --> 00:26:07,403
How do you feel now?

482
00:26:07,603 --> 00:26:08,484
Can you hear me?

483
00:26:09,363 --> 00:26:09,883
Shishi.

484
00:26:10,603 --> 00:26:11,244
Yu Shishi.

485
00:26:13,484 --> 00:26:14,883
Yu Shishi, you're silly.

486
00:26:16,244 --> 00:26:16,924
You shouldn't have come

487
00:26:16,964 --> 00:26:17,524
to Huining.

488
00:26:18,083 --> 00:26:19,204
You shouldn't have followed me.

489
00:26:19,643 --> 00:26:20,284
You're right.

490
00:26:20,603 --> 00:26:21,603
I'm a scoundrel, and I owe you a lot.

491
00:26:21,764 --> 00:26:22,363
Please wake up.

492
00:26:22,684 --> 00:26:23,204
How can you claim it back from me

493
00:26:23,323 --> 00:26:23,924
if you don't wake up?

494
00:26:24,004 --> 00:26:24,643
Yu Shishi.

495
00:26:25,244 --> 00:26:25,843
Wake up.

496
00:26:26,924 --> 00:26:27,444
Shishi.

497
00:26:30,803 --> 00:26:32,083
Huo Yanzong.

498
00:26:32,684 --> 00:26:34,563
Stop shaking me.

499
00:26:35,363 --> 00:26:35,803
You're awake.

500
00:26:36,444 --> 00:26:37,163
How do you feel now?

501
00:26:38,643 --> 00:26:39,603
I'll take you to the hospital now.

502
00:26:42,044 --> 00:26:42,764
Huo Yanzong.

503
00:26:43,964 --> 00:26:45,764
Once you meet with Xu Lai,

504
00:26:46,004 --> 00:26:47,724
you must return to Huaigang with me

505
00:26:49,403 --> 00:26:50,924
whether or not
she's willing to go with you.

506
00:26:51,724 --> 00:26:52,363
All right?

507
00:26:52,643 --> 00:26:53,643
Okay, I promise you.

508
00:26:53,964 --> 00:26:54,643
Also,

509
00:26:55,524 --> 00:26:57,123
don't ever disappear without a word.

510
00:26:57,803 --> 00:26:59,403
Don't leave me again.

511
00:26:59,403 --> 00:27:00,444
All right. You shouldn't talk much now.

512
00:27:00,803 --> 00:27:01,724
I'll take you to the hospital.

513
00:27:03,083 --> 00:27:03,764
Don't fall asleep.

514
00:27:04,284 --> 00:27:05,044
Please don't fall asleep.

515
00:27:18,123 --> 00:27:18,684
Shishi.

516
00:27:20,123 --> 00:27:20,964
Hold out.

517
00:27:23,284 --> 00:27:24,004
Hold out.

518
00:27:53,643 --> 00:27:54,403
Hold out.

519
00:28:01,800 --> 00:28:04,680
(Huaigang Fire Rescue)

520
00:28:04,684 --> 00:28:05,244
Hurry.

521
00:28:08,044 --> 00:28:08,444
Come.

522
00:28:08,883 --> 00:28:09,484
Hurry, Tao.

523
00:28:09,724 --> 00:28:10,524
Coming. Careful.

524
00:28:10,924 --> 00:28:11,764
Come.

525
00:28:12,684 --> 00:28:13,643
Be careful.

526
00:28:13,883 --> 00:28:14,284
Let's go.

527
00:28:14,323 --> 00:28:14,883
Are you all right?

528
00:28:14,960 --> 00:28:17,180
(Disaster Relief)

529
00:28:20,180 --> 00:28:25,080
(Fire Rescue)

530
00:28:27,764 --> 00:28:28,083
Come on.

531
00:28:28,284 --> 00:28:28,643
Give me a hand.

532
00:28:28,803 --> 00:28:29,044
Here.

533
00:28:29,284 --> 00:28:29,724
Hurry up.

534
00:28:31,964 --> 00:28:32,323
Is it okay?

535
00:28:33,724 --> 00:28:34,403
Slowly.

536
00:28:40,444 --> 00:28:41,883
We've brought
the injured here. Let's go.

537
00:28:42,123 --> 00:28:42,964
Hold on.

538
00:28:43,563 --> 00:28:44,964
Can you please take me
to Mofang Town with you?

539
00:28:45,803 --> 00:28:46,484
I want to follow you.

540
00:28:47,163 --> 00:28:47,924
You want to follow us?

541
00:28:48,924 --> 00:28:49,724
I know you.

542
00:28:50,363 --> 00:28:51,444
You're the team members

543
00:28:51,603 --> 00:28:52,684
of Captain Jin Shichuan, right?

544
00:28:53,924 --> 00:28:54,764
I'm looking for Xu Lai.

545
00:28:58,843 --> 00:28:59,363
Let's go.

546
00:28:59,524 --> 00:29:00,044
Thank you.

547
00:29:24,323 --> 00:29:24,803
Nurse.

548
00:29:25,524 --> 00:29:25,964
You're awake.

549
00:29:26,244 --> 00:29:26,843
Where's the guy

550
00:29:27,044 --> 00:29:28,524
who came with me?

551
00:29:28,964 --> 00:29:29,524
Who's it?

552
00:29:31,083 --> 00:29:31,843
Do you mean the rescue team?

553
00:29:31,924 --> 00:29:32,603
They've left.

554
00:29:36,204 --> 00:29:36,563
Wait.

555
00:29:36,803 --> 00:29:38,363
You can't get up now.

556
00:29:38,843 --> 00:29:40,924
Only the rescue team was here?

557
00:29:42,403 --> 00:29:43,284
It shouldn't be.

558
00:29:46,323 --> 00:29:47,964
Did something happen to him?

559
00:29:48,603 --> 00:29:49,244
I remember now.

560
00:29:49,484 --> 00:29:50,204
There was one guy.

561
00:29:50,684 --> 00:29:51,643
But he didn't enter the kiosk

562
00:29:51,764 --> 00:29:52,444
and left.

563
00:29:55,724 --> 00:29:57,123
He just left?

564
00:30:06,924 --> 00:30:08,643
Wait. Don't cry.

565
00:30:09,044 --> 00:30:10,044
He was fine.

566
00:30:12,964 --> 00:30:14,524
Yes, I don't have to cry.

567
00:30:15,403 --> 00:30:16,843
Thank you. Please don't let me keep you.

568
00:30:38,284 --> 00:30:39,044
Also,

569
00:30:39,724 --> 00:30:41,444
don't ever disappear without a word.

570
00:30:41,964 --> 00:30:43,524
Don't leave me again.

571
00:30:43,764 --> 00:30:45,123
All right. You shouldn't talk much now.

572
00:30:45,163 --> 00:30:46,083
I'll take you to the hospital.

573
00:30:55,843 --> 00:30:57,323
Huo Yanzong, liar.

574
00:30:58,484 --> 00:31:00,764
You promised not to abandon me.

575
00:31:04,180 --> 00:31:08,400
(Huaigang Fire Rescue)

576
00:31:12,980 --> 00:31:13,980
(Han Fang)

577
00:31:16,284 --> 00:31:16,724
Hello.

578
00:31:17,524 --> 00:31:17,843
(Hello.)

