00:31:21,363 --> 00:31:22,563
(have all been dispatched)

582
00:31:22,643 --> 00:31:23,403
(under the name of Yunkai.)

583
00:31:23,484 --> 00:31:25,444
(They'll arrive at the disaster area
the day after tomorrow.)

584
00:31:26,724 --> 00:31:27,204
Okay.

585
00:31:28,524 --> 00:31:28,924
(By the way,)

586
00:31:29,044 --> 00:31:30,044
(when are you coming back?)

587
00:31:33,964 --> 00:31:35,204
I can't return at the moment.

588
00:31:36,083 --> 00:31:37,083
I still can't find Xu Lai.

589
00:31:38,004 --> 00:31:38,524
(Well, then.)

590
00:31:39,163 --> 00:31:39,843
(I won't persuade you.)

591
00:31:40,643 --> 00:31:41,524
(Take care of yourself.)

592
00:31:42,444 --> 00:31:43,603
Okay, that's it then.

593
00:31:50,964 --> 00:31:52,484
(Don't ever disappear without a word.)

594
00:31:53,323 --> 00:31:54,643
(Don't leave me again.)

595
00:32:17,484 --> 00:32:19,484
Finally, you answered my call.

596
00:32:19,724 --> 00:32:20,244
I couldn't reach you

597
00:32:20,244 --> 00:32:20,883
all these days.

598
00:32:20,924 --> 00:32:21,843
I thought something happened to you.

599
00:32:21,964 --> 00:32:23,323
Do you know how deeply
I've been worried about you?

600
00:32:24,083 --> 00:32:24,883
I'm fine.

601
00:32:26,284 --> 00:32:27,044
What a relief.

602
00:32:27,684 --> 00:32:29,803
By the way, you said you were leaving
for a relaxing trip.

603
00:32:29,964 --> 00:32:31,123
Have you reached your destination?

604
00:32:33,083 --> 00:32:33,803
Yes.

605
00:32:35,843 --> 00:32:36,924
I've arrived at the finish point too.

606
00:32:38,524 --> 00:32:39,764
I have found my closure.

607
00:32:47,964 --> 00:32:49,764
(The trip is completely over.)

608
00:32:51,123 --> 00:32:52,323
(Time to go back.)

609
00:33:04,524 --> 00:33:05,004
(Hello, doctor.)

610
00:33:05,204 --> 00:33:05,643
(Hello.)

611
00:33:06,123 --> 00:33:06,764
