612
00:33:07,163 --> 00:33:07,524
(if there's a patient)

613
00:33:07,524 --> 00:33:08,363
(named Yu Shishi.)

614
00:33:08,964 --> 00:33:09,524
Yes, there is.

615
00:33:09,803 --> 00:33:10,603
(How's her situation now?)

616
00:33:11,083 --> 00:33:12,163
She has regained consciousness,

617
00:33:12,403 --> 00:33:13,444
but she still needs rest.

618
00:33:16,764 --> 00:33:17,524
(Do you have any messages)

619
00:33:17,524 --> 00:33:18,643
(I can convey to her?)

620
00:33:21,004 --> 00:33:21,524
No.

621
00:33:22,044 --> 00:33:23,123
Please take care of her.

622
00:33:23,323 --> 00:33:23,964
Thank you.

623
00:33:25,820 --> 00:33:31,080
(Let's Overcome Hardships Together)

624
00:33:31,964 --> 00:33:33,643
I just received instructions
from the command center.

625
00:33:34,363 --> 00:33:35,004
We,

626
00:33:35,004 --> 00:33:36,403
the Huaigang Earthquake Relief Team,

627
00:33:36,843 --> 00:33:38,323
have been assigned to rescue
Lianhua Village.

628
00:33:38,924 --> 00:33:40,724
There was a secondary collapse

629
00:33:40,924 --> 00:33:42,964
after the earthquake in Lianhua village.

630
00:33:43,603 --> 00:33:44,924
The internal building structures

631
00:33:44,964 --> 00:33:46,444
are extremely fragile now.

632
00:33:47,484 --> 00:33:48,284
There might be a risk

633
00:33:48,563 --> 00:33:49,924
of structural displacement.

634
00:33:50,363 --> 00:33:51,204
If we're not careful,

635
00:33:51,764 --> 00:33:53,004
we could be trapped inside too.

636
00:33:53,444 --> 00:33:53,964
So,

637
00:33:53,964 --> 00:33:55,123
you ought to be highly cautious

638
00:33:55,323 --> 00:33:56,163
when you perform the rescue task.

639
00:33:56,323 --> 00:33:56,883
- Yes.
- Yes.

640
00:33:58,563 --> 00:33:59,603
(All rescue units, attention.)

641
00:33:59,684 --> 00:34:00,603
(Someone is spotted stealing drugs)

642
00:34:00,603 --> 00:34:01,363
(from the first-aid kiosk.)

643
00:34:01,883 --> 00:34:03,323
(According to
the on-site medical staff,)

644
00:34:03,323 --> 00:34:04,563
(it's suspected to be a drug user.)

645
00:34:04,643 --> 00:34:05,563
(If you find this person,)

646
00:34:05,803 --> 00:34:06,603
(please report it immediately.)

647
00:34:08,484 --> 00:34:09,683
Team No. 27, copy that.

648
00:34:10,163 --> 00:34:10,723
How is it possible

649
00:34:10,804 --> 00:34:11,723
that someone would use drugs here?

650
00:34:12,563 --> 00:34:13,404
I remember that now.

651
00:34:14,364 --> 00:34:14,844
I heard

652
00:34:15,004 --> 00:34:16,004
that a resident's son

653
00:34:16,563 --> 00:34:17,723
was just released from the rehab center.

654
00:34:18,324 --> 00:34:19,484
Probably he's from Lianhua Village.

655
00:34:21,643 --> 00:34:22,364
Stay alert, everyone.

656
00:34:22,924 --> 00:34:23,243
Let's go.

657
00:34:23,364 --> 00:34:24,044
- Yes.
- Yes.

658
00:34:29,884 --> 00:34:30,924
Please be very careful.

659
00:34:33,683 --> 00:34:34,324
Don't worry.

660
00:34:36,324 --> 00:34:37,924
I have the lucky charm with me.

661
00:34:39,123 --> 00:34:40,083
It will protect me.

662
00:34:40,404 --> 00:34:41,444
I will be safe.

663
00:34:42,643 --> 00:34:43,243
I'll wait for you.

664
00:34:44,924 --> 00:34:45,444
Yes, madam.

665
00:34:55,440 --> 00:35:05,760
(Huaigang Fire Rescue,
Search and Rescue)

666
00:35:05,763 --> 00:35:06,203
Get off.

667
00:35:11,563 --> 00:35:12,044
Captain Jin.

668
00:35:12,364 --> 00:35:13,643
The on-site assessment is done.

669
00:35:13,844 --> 00:35:14,683
Put on protection kits

670
00:35:14,844 --> 00:35:15,484
and be careful.

671
00:35:15,804 --> 00:35:16,283
Thank you.

672
00:35:46,243 --> 00:35:46,763
Zhang Yang.

673
00:35:47,924 --> 00:35:48,444
Come over.

674
00:35:57,203 --> 00:35:58,044
Bring the detector here.

675
00:35:58,203 --> 00:35:58,723
Hurry.

676
00:36:09,444 --> 00:36:09,924
Stretch it forward.

677
00:36:10,563 --> 00:36:11,083
In that direction.

678
00:36:11,683 --> 00:36:12,203
Okay.

679
00:36:19,083 --> 00:36:19,763
Deeper.

680
00:36:24,804 --> 00:36:25,683
Can you see it?

681
00:36:25,964 --> 00:36:26,524
Here.

682
00:36:27,083 --> 00:36:27,763
I saw it.

683
00:36:32,364 --> 00:36:32,844
Call him.

684
00:36:34,123 --> 00:36:34,924
Someone below there,

685
00:36:35,404 --> 00:36:36,844
can you hear me?

686
00:36:44,163 --> 00:36:45,163
Can you hear me?

687
00:36:45,643 --> 00:36:47,324
If you hear me, move your body.

688
00:36:53,243 --> 00:36:53,763
No response.

689
00:36:57,243 --> 00:36:57,643
Captain Jin.

690
00:36:58,083 --> 00:36:58,723
We have a situation here.

691
00:36:59,524 --> 00:37:00,404
There's a person below,

692
00:37:00,763 --> 00:37:02,243
and the detector shows signs of life.

693
00:37:02,404 --> 00:37:03,163
