698
00:37:19,044 --> 00:37:20,044
If we go from below,

699
00:37:20,243 --> 00:37:21,324
there'll be a collapse.

700
00:37:22,683 --> 00:37:23,283
Liu Xu.

701
00:37:23,603 --> 00:37:24,404
Open up a rescue entry

702
00:37:24,643 --> 00:37:25,603
from the side.

703
00:37:26,924 --> 00:37:28,123
Zhang Yang, Dapeng.

704
00:37:28,243 --> 00:37:30,683
Get the small air blower
to supply air inside.

705
00:37:31,763 --> 00:37:33,283
You stay here and monitor.

706
00:37:33,683 --> 00:37:34,804
- Yes.
- Yes.

707
00:38:03,723 --> 00:38:04,163
Captain Jin.

708
00:38:04,643 --> 00:38:05,364
Something's wrong.

709
00:38:12,723 --> 00:38:13,603
Is this the junkie

710
00:38:13,603 --> 00:38:14,404
