711
00:38:15,083 --> 00:38:15,723
Save him first.

712
00:38:18,203 --> 00:38:18,964
What's the situation below?

713
00:38:19,643 --> 00:38:20,444
The structure isn't stable.

714
00:38:20,844 --> 00:38:22,044
It's risky if we go in like this.

715
00:38:22,603 --> 00:38:23,563
We should wait for the excavator

716
00:38:23,763 --> 00:38:24,804
