717
00:38:24,924 --> 00:38:25,723
It's safer.

718
00:38:25,804 --> 00:38:26,324
We're running out of time.

719
00:38:26,763 --> 00:38:27,964
There'll be a collapse at any time.

720
00:38:28,723 --> 00:38:29,683
Organize the rescue immediately.

721
00:38:30,844 --> 00:38:31,484
Captain Jin.

722
00:38:31,844 --> 00:38:32,924
