723
00:38:33,324 --> 00:38:33,844
Captain Jin.

724
00:38:34,563 --> 00:38:35,243
I think we should wait.

725
00:38:36,324 --> 00:38:37,083
We must seize

726
00:38:37,083 --> 00:38:38,163
