727
00:38:38,763 --> 00:38:39,683
I'll go in from the side.

728
00:38:40,123 --> 00:38:40,524
Zhang Yang.

729
00:38:40,804 --> 00:38:41,203
Come with me.

730
00:38:41,444 --> 00:38:41,763
Yes.

731
00:38:41,844 --> 00:38:42,683
You stay here.

732
00:38:43,243 --> 00:38:43,924
- Yes.
- Yes.

733
00:38:44,083 --> 00:38:44,844
Be careful.

734
00:38:55,163 --> 00:38:55,844
Slowly. Captain Jin.

