739
00:39:07,844 --> 00:39:08,283
Captain Jin.

740
00:39:10,404 --> 00:39:10,884
Be careful.

741
00:40:02,603 --> 00:40:03,324
Are you all right?

742
00:40:04,243 --> 00:40:05,004
Don't fall asleep.

743
00:40:05,524 --> 00:40:06,243
Stay awake.

744
00:40:07,804 --> 00:40:09,484
Don't catch me.

